With the `processor` state now correctly typed, the `as any` type assertion is no longer necessary, which improves type safety.

```suggestion
        const newProcessor = new MessageProcessor([minimalCatalog], async (action: any) => {
          setLogs((l) => [...l, {time: new Date().toLocaleTimeString(), action}]);
        });
```
